        "text": "1 Kings 5:13-14",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", it would seem that a modified service of forced labor for one-third of each year was not regarded as reducing those who were subject to it to the condition of bondmen.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
